quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  26,52,Nos inspired Moses Travel My servus vos pursued
  26,53,Pharaoh sent to oppidum callers
  26,54,(Proclaiming) Hoc est parvulus gang
  26,55,They statim opposing nos
  26,56,all beware de them
  26,57,Consequently nos deprived them de gardens fons
  26,58,Ac treasures ac prenobilis position
  26,59,Tunc nos factus it inheritance Infans Israel
  26,60,They pursued them east
  26,61,When ambo parties vide each alius Moses' people dictus Nos caught
  26,62,He non dictus via My Dominus est me; He guide me
  26,63,Nos tunc inspired Moses Strike sea tuus staff whereupon it parted Each part est major collis
  26,64,Nos tunc delivered them totus
  26,65,Nos sic saved Moses totus those est eum
  26,66,Nos drowned others
  26,67,Hoc est sufficient proof multus people non est believers
  26,68,multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful
  26,69,Narrate to them Abraham's history
  26,70,He dictus to his patris his people Quod hoc vos est worshipping
  26,71,They dictus Nos worship statues; nos est totally devoted to them
  26,72,He dictus they hear vos when vos implore
  26,73,they benefit vos Potuit harm vos
  26,74,They non dictus nos invenit noster parentes perfecit hoc
  26,75,He dictus Perfecit vos vide these idols vos worship
  26,76,Vos tuus patres
  26,77,Ego est them pro ego devoted unus Dominus universe
  26,78,Unus created me guided me
  26,79,Unus feeds me aqua me
  26,80,Ac when ego get aeger He heals me
  26,81,Unus puts me decessus tunc brings me back vita
  26,82,Unus qui hopefully forgive my sins Feria Judgment
  26,83,My Dominus grant me wisdom include me cum the righteous
  26,84,Let example ego set pro the future generations est bonus
  26,85,Factus me 1 inheritors blissful Paradise
  26,86,Ac forgive my patris pro he iit astray
  26,87,Non forsake me Feria Resurrection
  26,88,Ut est feria when nec moneta nor infans help
  26,89,Unus those advenit DEUS their whole heart (testimentum saved)
  26,90,Paradise presens the righteous
  26,91,Hell set strayers
  26,92,They asked Ubi est idols vos worshipped
  26,93,beside DEUS? they help vos statim? they help
  26,94,They thrown therein unus strayers
  26,95,totus de Satan's militis
  26,96,They dictus prout they feud therein
  26,97,De DEUS nos est far astray
  26,98,Quam nos set vos could rank Dominus universe
  26,99,Those misled nos est wicked
  26,100,Nunc nos non habet intercessors
  26,101,Nor single clausum friend
  26,102,Unus nos get alias chance nos tunc believe
  26,103,Hoc est bonus lesson. Multus people non est believers
  26,104,Tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful
  26,105,people Noah disbelieved messengers
  26,106,Their frater Noah dictus to them vos non est righteous
  26,107,Ego est honest messenger vos
  26,108,Vos reverence DEUS obey me
  26,109,Ego non ask vos any wage My wage advenit ex Dominus universe
  26,110,Vos reverence DEUS obey me